Engineered for those who move between worlds, TheROCKER delivers long-distance comfort, confident grip, and breathable durability across mixed terrain.

column47: TuneLug™ Outsole: Co-engineered with Vibram®, the TuneLug™ outsole combines Megagrip™ for outstanding grip on wet and dry surfaces and Litebase™ for reduced weight. The conical lug geometry is custom-designed for directional control, while the 360° wrap provides added sidewall traction and durability.
column48: Rippy™ 66 Monomesh: This high-tenacity material stabilizes your foot, managing moisture and ensuring a secure, comfortable fit, so you stay locked in as you take on the trail.
column49: Euforia™ Super Foam:  Euforia™ is SATISFY’s proprietary midsole foam, blending PEBA and EVA to deliver soft, stable cushioning for long-distance efforts. Tuned for a smooth, consistent ride across road and trail, it’s designed to feel good no matter where the run takes you.
